flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow\"><div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-snug\">TV Wall Mounting</h3></div><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Professional mounting for all TV sizes with tilt, swivel, or ceiling brackets. Clean finish and secure installation.</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-6\"><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Swivel &amp; tilt brackets</li><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Cable management</li><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Sound bar &amp; home theater setup</li></ul></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-200 pt-4 flex justify-between items-center\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider\">From</span><span class=\"text-lg font-black text-blue-600\">Kes 1,500</span></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-slate-200 flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow\"><div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-snug\">Starlink Internet Setup</h3></div><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Get high-speed Starlink internet professionally installed for homes and businesses. Fast, reliable, and secure.</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-6\"><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Mounting &amp; alignment</li><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Router configuration</li><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Signal optimization</li></ul></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-200 pt-4 flex justify-between items-center\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider\">From</span><span class=\"text-lg font-black text-blue-600\">Kes 4,000</span></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-slate-200 flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow\"><div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-snug\">CCTV &amp; Security Systems</h3></div><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Secure your home or business with CCTV cameras, electric fences, and alarm systems. Remote monitoring available.</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 mb-6\"><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Camera installation &amp; servicing</li><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Electric fence setup</li><li class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\"></span>Home security systems</li></ul></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-200 pt-4 flex justify-between items-center\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider\">From</span><span class=\"text-lg font-black text-blue-600\">Kes 5,000</span></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-slate-200 flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow\"><div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-snug\">Central Dish &amp; Aerial</h3></div><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Centralized dish and aerial installations for apartments and estates. Clean, efficient, and cost-effective solutions.<